title: The 5th Dimension
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Pizza, Juice bar, Beer/Wine
description: A vegetarian place with a smoothie and juice bar, situated on the top of a building on the 2nd floor (you have to look for it). Relaxed atmosphere with view of the lake. Has Wi-Fi. Shows cult movies on Sunday nights. Also is a venue for hosting documentaries (and can order food with notice).
streetAddress: 8th Calle, turn right from Panajachel Dock
